  "title": "Locum Speech Therapist (Community Hospital, East)",
  "description": "<p>We are actively hiring for a client in a Community Hospital setting in Singapore and we wish to invite interested therapist to apply the role.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Code: SCHE05/08/ST</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Locum Speech Therapist - 6 months</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide speech therapy and swallowing assessment / intervention to patients</li>\n  <li>Maximize patients' speech and swallowing potential and improve quality of life</li>\n  <li>Formulate and implement appropriate goals and treatment plans</li>\n  <li>Assess diagnose, manage, and treat swallowing, speech impairments</li>\n  <li>Work as part of a multi-disciplinary team</li>\n  <li>Regular review of planned goals and modification of goals in accordance of SMART goals to ensure effective therapy is being delivered</li>\n  <li>Plan future follow up or discharge from ST services based on patients’ performance.</li>\n  <li>Conduct relevant caregiver training effectively to stakeholders to ensure patients care is carried out at home</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Project Details</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>5 full days per week (9.00am - 5.00pm), 8 hours per visit</li>\n  <li>Projected Commencement: from December 2025 - January 2026 onwards (Start date is negotiable)</li>\n  <li>Competitive hourly remuneration covered with Medical Malpractice + Complimentary access to CPE events conducted by Pacific Rehab Group</li>\n  <li>Bachelor or Masters in Speech Therapy</li>\n  <li>Must be a Fully Registered AHPC ( Singapore )</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Drop in your CV to: hr@pacificrehab.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Or WhatsApp 8022 6814</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Quick SIGN UP here : https://form.jotform.com/250558451726461</strong></p>",
