    "description": "<p><strong>Pacific Rehab Group</strong> is a Singapore-based Allied Health Professionals Hub that specializes in providing placement and staffing solutions for healthcare organizations. Our services focus on connecting highly qualified professionals, such as physiotherapists, occupational therapists, speech therapists, and medical specialists, with various healthcare settings including hospitals, community care facilities, and private clinics. We offer flexible placement options, including permanent, locum, and contract positions, tailored to meet the specific needs of healthcare providers. Our commitment is to deliver exceptional care through our network of skilled professionals, enhancing patient outcomes and supporting the healthcare community.</p>",
